      br\xF3mos, meaning \"stench\") is a chemical element with symbol Br, and atomic
      number 35. It is a halogen. The element was isolated independently by two chemists,
      Carl Jacob L\xF6wig and Antoine Jerome Balard, in 1825\u20131826."
    boil: 332
